    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Hi Molly,<br />How exciting to see Delancey being so successful! Just to let you know I posted a plum and pear crumble recipe inspired by yours on my latest Tasty Diaries newsletter:<br /><a href="http://www.tastydiaries.com/TD/Current_newsletter.html" rel="nofollow ugc">http://www.tastydiaries.com/TD/Current_newsletter.html</a></p>
<p>Scroll down the newsletter, you will find it. I give you credit of course on the recipe page!! My main changes are less cinnamon (in Europe we are less used to the stuff) and I am softening the fruits a bit in a pan before using them in the crumble. It makes them juicier. Have look and let me know if you like it!<br />Anne-Laure x</p>
