      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-19723' data-commentid="19723" data-postid="931" data-belowelement="comment-19723" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Ena" aria-label='Reply to Ena'>Reply</a>    </div>
  </li><!-- #comment-## -->
  <li id="comment-19725" class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn">Ena</cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2009/09/what-i-do-now/#comment-19725"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2011-09-17T21:27:24-04:00">Saturday, September 17, 2011 at 9:27 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Made it today and it is really good. I loved the addition of candied ginger. Next time I will add more plums, though, as I love fruit to be abundant in crumbles.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-19725' data-commentid="19725" data-postid="931" data-belowelement="comment-19725" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Ena" aria-label='Reply to Ena'>Reply</a>    </div>
